headline: Where are Lumber Prices Heading into the 2026 Construction Season?
summary: As spring approaches, physical lumber futures for May delivery are trading just below $600 per 1,000 board feet. Since lumber futures typically reach seasonally high prices in spring and early summer, now could be the perfect time to add lumber exposure to your portfolio.
